target: It was my pleasure! Enjoy your stay!
context: <user>  I'm looking for a place to stay while in Cambridge. What is available in the west area that has free wifi? <system>  There are 4 hotels to choose from. I can recommend Finches Bed and Breakfast. It's a cheap 4 star guesthouse. Does that work? <user>  I need a guesthouse with a star rating of 0. <system>  I'm sorry, there are no 0 star guesthouses, would you like to try something else? <user>  Is there a guesthouse located in the centre with free wifi? <system>  El Shaddai fits your needs. Would you like me to reserve a room? <user>  Does that have free parking? <system>  Yes it does. It's cheap and has free parking.<user>  Thanks for the info. I also need to look for a train. Can you look that up? <system>  Absolutely. Let me start by asking you what your departure and destination locations will be?<user>  I'm going from Cambridge to Ely. <system>  Great! What day and time to you want to travel on?<user>  I would like to travel on Tuesday and leave sometime after 16:30. <system>  TR7733 leaves at 17:50. May I book that for you?<user>  That sounds good. Please get me tickets for six people. <system>  The Booking was successful, the total fee is 26.4 GBP payable at the station . Reference number is : TO3Z8A06 .<user>  Thank you very much. <system>  Can I be of further assistance today?<user>  No, you've been a great help mate. Thanks for everything! <system>
